        ": مَنْ قَرَأَ سُورَهَ الْعَادِیَاتِ وَ أَدْمَنَ قِرَاءَتَهَا بَعَثَهُ اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ مَعَ أَمِیرِ الْمُؤْمِنِینَ ع یَوْمَ الْقِیَامَهِ خَاصَّهً وَ کَانَ فِی حَجْرِهِ وَ رُفَقَائِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1. From the previous chain from Abi Abdillah al-Muwafi [al-Mu’min] from Ibn Muskan from Sulayman b. Khalid from Abi Abdillah (a.s.) who said: One who recites it, would be with Ali (a.s.) on the Day of Judgment and would be among his special companions."
